                          <li><strong>Categories</strong>: Lists all categories
                            with post counts, styled with Bootstrap badges for
                            clarity.</li>
                          <li><strong>Recent Posts</strong>: Displays the 5 most
                            recent published posts with titles and thumbnails
                            (if available), encouraging exploration of new
                            content.</li>
                          <li><strong>Popular Posts</strong>: Shows the 5 posts
                            with the highest view counts, highlighting trending
                            content.</li>
                          <li><strong>Random Posts</strong>: Suggests 3 random
                            published posts using MongoDB’s $sample operator,
                            adding variety to content discovery.</li>
                          <li><strong>User Stats (Logged-in Users)</strong>: For
                            authenticated users, displays their post count,
